A[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="719" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/f43b53b0-909f-11ea-87fd-d8d721459924" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Engadget Podcast]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Engadget Podcast]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA['GTA VI' hacker leaked footage using a Fire TV Stick in a budget UK hotel room]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在电影中，黑客通常坐在一张大桌子前，面前摆着大量尖端技术。在现实生活中，事实证明，您只需要一个 Amazon Fire TV 棒、智能手机、键盘和鼠标，就可以窃取和<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rockstar-grand-theft-auto-6-leak-155755703.html">泄露未发行游戏（例如备受期待的<em>侠盗猎车手 IV）</em>中的剪辑</a>。<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-66549159"><em>据 BBC 新闻</em>报道，</a>这正是黑客组织<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/uk-police-charge-two-teens-in-connection-with-lapsus-hacking-group-case-113521533.html">Lapsus$</a>成员 Arion Kurtaj 在因涉嫌黑客攻击 NVIDIA 而被保释期间所做的事情。</p><p>这位 18 岁的少年潜入了<em>《GTA VI》</em>的制作公司 Rockstar Games，甚至在该公司的 Slack 频道中宣布自己是“攻击者”。案发现场？一家英国Travelodge酒店的官员把他安置在了这里。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>黑客“人肉搜索”了库尔塔杰，在网上发布了他及其家人的详细信息，并危及了他的安全，库尔塔杰被转移到了酒店。在那里，他不被允许访问互联网——他使用 Fire TV Stick 来上网。</p><p>经过七周的审判后，库尔塔吉的非法行为的更多细节被公开，他被判犯有黑客攻击 Rockstar、neobank Revolut 和<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/uber-hack-targeted-contractor-lapsus-192339707.html">Uber</a>的罪名。一名 17 岁的青少年也被定罪，但与库尔塔杰不同的是，他仍处于保释状态。这两个人都是自闭症患者，精神科医生认为他们没有资格接受审判。这意味着陪审团只有在认为犯罪确实发生时才会介入，而不是在犯罪意图存在的情况下进行介入。</p><p> Lapsus$ 在法庭上被称为“数字强盗”组织，据信主要由来自巴西和英国的青少年组成——Kurtaj 和这名未透露姓名的 17 岁青少年是在英国被捕的七名成员中的两人。据称，2021 年至 2022 年间，Lapsus$ 还对三星、T-Mobile 和<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-okta-investigating-attack-lapsus-hacking-group-120541942.html">微软</a>进行了黑客攻击。尽管该组织要求赎金，但尚不清楚它从这些漏洞中获利了多少（如果有的话）。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/gta-vi-hacker-leaked-footage-using-a-fire-tv-stick-in-a-budget-uk-hotel-room-121548381 .html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/gta-vi-hacker-leaked-footage-using-a-fire-tv-stick-in-a-budget-uk-hotel-room-121548381.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 323203f2-75b4-4611-99d6-d51efe3ce5d7</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 25 Aug 2023 12:15:48 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692972189</ingested><modified> 2023-08-25T14:03:12+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Society & Culture]]></category><category><![CDATA[Crime & Justice]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="2362" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-07/6dae5ac0-0db8-11ed-bce7-e4f8ed4e4853" width="3543"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2362" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-07/6dae5ac0-0db8-11ed-bce7-e4f8ed4e4853" width="3543"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Grand Theft Auto logo displayed on a laptop screen and a gamepad are seen in this illustration photo taken in Krakow, Poland on September 21, 2021. (Photo by Jakub Porzycki/NurPhoto via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Video Games Brands Photo Illustrations]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Solar Orbiter spacecraft may have discovered what powers solar winds]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我们知道太阳会喷出太阳风，但这些带电粒子流的起源仍然是个谜，并且在过去几十年中一直是众多研究的主题。然而，欧空局和美国宇航局<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/esa-nasa-solar-orbiter-closest-sun-images-155421587.html">太阳轨道飞行器</a>上的极紫外成像仪（EUI）去年<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.esa.int/Science_Exploration/Space_Science/Solar_Orbiter/Solar_Orbiter_discovers_tiny_jets_that_could_power_the_solar_wind">拍摄的图像</a>可能最终为我们提供了解释这些风的动力<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Nature Research;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=c6c965be-a8ea-473d-89f4-9754f2675a60&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Nature+Research&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJjNmM5NjViZS1hOGVhLTQ3M2QtODlmNC05NzU0ZjI2NzVhNjAiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubmF0dXJlLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9kNDE1ODYtMDIzLTAyNjY4LTUiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImIzNThiZjU4LWY2ZWEtNGNiYy05Zjk0LWIwYjY5ODZhZTZkYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcXIICCMCwuG72SYJm9EG7bBZOLgNSiwnARLYE2IPBWS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-023-02668-5" class="rapid-with-clickid">所需的</a>知识。在<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.ade5801"><em>《科学》</em></a>杂志上发表的一篇论文中，一组研究人员描述了在航天器拍摄的图像中观察到大量喷流从太阳的黑暗区域（称为“日冕洞”）喷出。</p><p>研究小组称它们为“皮耀斑喷流”，因为它们所含的能量约为最大太阳耀斑产生的能量的万亿分之一。 These picoflare jets measure a few hundred kilometers in length, reach speeds of around 100 kilometers per second and only last between 20 and 100 seconds. Still, the researchers believe they have the power to emit enough high-temperature plasma to be considered a substantial source of our system&#39;s solar winds. While Coronal holes have long been known as source regions for the phenomenon, scientists are still trying to figure out the mechanism of how plasma streams emerge from them exactly. This discovery could finally be the answer they&#39;d been seeking for years.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Lakshmi Pradeep Chitta, the study&#39;s primary author from the Max Planck Institute for Solar System Research, told <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.space.com/rapid-tiny-jets-solar-orbiter-wind-power"><em>Space</em></a> : &quot;The picoflare jets that we observed are the smallest, and energetically the weakest, type of jets in the solar corona that were not observed before...Still, the energy content of a single picoflare jet that lives for about 1 minute is equal to the average power consumed by about 10,000 households in the UK over an entire year.&quot;</p><p> Chitta&#39;s team will continue monitoring coronal holes and other potential sources of solar winds using the Solar Orbiter going forward. In addition to gathering data that may finally give us answers about the plasma flows responsible for producing auroras here on our planet, their observations could also shed light on why the sun&#39;s corona or atmosphere is much, much hotter than its surface. </p><div id="04b9f609947b492599521334e81aea48"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KrjW320d_88?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-solar-orbiter-spacecraft-may-have-discovered-what-powers-solar-winds-114504839.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-solar-orbiter-spacecraft-may-have-discovered-what-powers-solar-winds-114504839.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><gui